# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OMS uses PER-APP environment files (more robust for Prisma + Vite).
#
#   Backend  →  apps/api/.env   (copy from apps/api/.env.example)
#   Frontend →  apps/web/.env   (copy from apps/web/.env.example)
#
# This root file is intentionally just a pointer. See the two app examples.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
